Static analysis libraries and tooling for Terraform Provider code.
Ratchet is a tool for improving the security of CI/CD workflows by automating 
the process of pinning and unpinning upstream versions. It's like Bundler, 
Cargo, Go modules, NPM, Pip, or Yarn, but for CI/CD workflows. Ratchet 
supports: Circle CI, GitHub Actions, Google Cloud Build.

WWW: https://github.com/sethvargo/ratchet
